==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Composed
<hw>Com*posed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Free from
agitation; calm; sedate; quiet; tranquil; self-possessed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The Mantuan there in sober triumph sate,⟦br⟧
<qex>Composed</qex> his posture, and his look sedate.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Com*pos"ed*ly</wf> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
-- <wf>Com*pos"ed*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Composer</ent>⟦br⟧
